snippet.title: Johnny Depp’s concert in Sweden faces boycott over Amber Heard abuse claims
snippet.description:
A social media campaign is calling on ticket buyers to boycott a Monday night concert by Johnny Depp's rock band, The Hollywood Vampires, in Stockholm amid the  the domestic abuse allegations from Amber Heard.
